      "body": "Hey Jane,\n\nHope you're doing well! As you might know, Alex's birthday is coming up next week, and we're planning a little surprise for him. Given your close friendship with Alex, I thought you might help us with some details. Could you provide any relevant information?\n\nThanks a lot!  \nMark\n"
